    <h1>Tokyo</h1>
    <p>Tokyo, the capital city of Japan, is a vibrant metropolis that perfectly blends modern innovation with traditional culture. It is one of the most technologically advanced cities in the world, famous for its towering skyscrapers, neon-lit streets, and efficient transportation system. At the same time, Tokyo preserves its rich history through ancient temples, peaceful gardens, and traditional festivals.</p>
    <p>Landmarks such as the Tokyo Tower, Shibuya Crossing, Senso-ji Temple, and the Imperial Palace showcase the cityâ€™s diverse character. Tokyo is also a global hub for fashion, cuisine, and technology, offering everything from world-class sushi restaurants to cutting-edge robotics. Whether exploring its bustling districts or serene shrines, visitors experience the perfect harmony of innovation, culture, and tradition that defines Tokyo.</p>



    